{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"title":"Base","content":["Preheat oven to 160°C. Grease sides and line base of a spring form tin (Ø 20 cm) with baking paper.","Place gingernuts, digestives and butter in mixing bowl then crush <b>15 sec\/speed 10<b>. Transfer to prepared tin and press down with back of a spoon forming a firm biscuit layer. Bake for 10 minutes (160°C) then set aside to cool. Meanwhile, clean mixing bowl and prepare filling."]},{"title":"Filling","content":["Place lime peelings and sugar in mixing bowl then grind <b>10 sec\/speed 9<b>.","Add sour cream, cream cheese and eggs then blend <b>20 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then blend again <b>10 sec\/speed 5<b>. Pour cheesecake mixture onto cooled biscuit base. Cover tin in aluminum foil then place in Varoma dish.","Place water in mixing bowl. Place covered Varoma into position then steam <b>60 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Check to see that cake is set in middle. If not, re-wrap and cook for a further <b>15-20 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Remove cake from Varoma and allow to cool in tin before placing in fridge for a minimum of 4 hours to set. Meanwhile, clean mixing bowl."]},{"title":"Mango and Passion Fruit Topping","content":["Once cheesecake is set, place sugar in mixing bowl and grind <b>10 sec\/speed 10<b>.","Cut 1 mango into pieces and add to mixing bowl. Blend <b>30 sec\/speed 5<b> <strong>-10, increasing speed gradually<\/strong>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then blend again <b>5 sec\/speed 5<b>.","Remove cheesecake from tin then pour mango purée over surface, spreading out evenly, letting it drizzle down sides. Cut remaining mango into long slices and arrange over purée layer. Scatter passion fruit pulp and seeds over top then serve chilled."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"Base","content":["50 g butter, diced, plus extra for greasing","75 g gingernut biscuits","75 g digestive biscuits"]},{"title":"Filling","content":["1 lime, thin peelings of skin only","150 g granulated sugar","140 g sour cream","400 g cream cheese (full fat)","4 medium eggs","1200 g water, for steaming"]},{"title":"Mango and Passion Fruit Topping","content":["30 g granulated sugar","2 ripe mango (destoned weight approx. 500 g)","1 passion fruit, pulp and seeds"]}],"id":"r125316","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-4Sp6Sj5usio\/XZWeokW773I\/AAAAAAAAe3I\/_1wj9oGdBZIscKEX0nDCIq-BASHSFi6SgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_dzzBVY_u-In1mpcl.png","title":"Mango, Passionfruit and Lime Cheesecake","publishedAt":"2016-08-29T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"5.6 g","fat":"31.1 g","uom":"per 1 slice","carbohydrates":"36.8 g","calories":"1877 kJ \/ 449 kcal"},"usefulItems":"spring form tin (Ø 20 cm), baking paper, aluminium foil, oven, refrigerator","basicInfo":["medium","25m","5h 35m","10 slices"]}